OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine
OL,6,Fevening with plenty of late sunshine.
OL,7,FStaying dry overnight with clear
OL,8,Fskies, though turning breezier by the
OL,9,Fmorning. Chilly overnight in the
OL,10,Fcountryside.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA fine, dry and sunny day
OL,13,Fahead. Remaining breezy, especially in
OL,14,Fthe south, which may take the edge off
OL,15,Fthe temperatures but feeling a warm in
OL,16,Fsheltered spots.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
