OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FRemaining dry, sunny and warm on
OL,7,FThursday. Lighter winds on Friday with
OL,8,Fmore sunshine making it feel even
OL,9,Fwarmer. Turning humid later with a
OL,10,Frisk of heavy showers on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
